Description_lang: Upon casting any spell, Sarkareth empowers his allies with the might of the Black dragons. This effect increases their damage done and movement speed by $s1%. Upon reaching $s3 applications, the target becomes immune to crowd controlling and interrupting effects.
AuraDescription_lang: Damage done increased by $s2%.Movement speed increased by $s1%.At $s3 stacks, the caster becomes immune to crowd controlling and interrupting effects.
